            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/messageui"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/photokit"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "title": "ResearchKit",
              "destination": "http://researchkit.org"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/sensorkit"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/speech"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Using any of these frameworks in an App Clip doesn’t result in compile-time errors, but their APIs return values that indicate unavailability, empty data, or error codes at runtime. For example, HealthKit’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/healthkit/hkhealthstore/1614180-ishealthdataavailable"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "false"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " when you call it from an App Clip."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Preserve User Privacy",
          "anchor": "3625586"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "App Clips come with limitations that help to protect user privacy and prevent user tracking across apps and App Clips, for example:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Functionality provided by "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/storekit/skadnetwork"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " isn’t available."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "App Clips can’t request authorization to track the user with "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apptrackingtransparency"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Both "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uidevice/1620015-name"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " and "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uidevice/1620059-identifierforvendor"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " return an empty string."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "App Clips can’t request continuous location access. However, you can call "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corelocation/cllocationmanager/1620562-requestwheninuseauthorization"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " to request the When In Use authorization, which resets automatically the next day at 4:00 a.m."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "App Clips can’t request the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/bundleresources/entitlements/com_apple_developer_pass-type-identifiers"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " to read passes stored in the Wallet app. However, if your App Clip contains functionality to add a pass to the Wallet app, you can check if this pass is already present. For more information, see "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "link",
                      "title": "Checking Whether a Pass Is in the Library",
                      "destination": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/UserExperience/Conceptual/PassKit_PG/Apps.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40012195-CH6-SW3"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "An App Clip can’t share data with any other app except its corresponding full app. For more information, see "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/app_clips/sharing_data_between_your_app_clip_and_your_full_app"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "App Clips also come with limitations that help protect user data. They can’t access:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Apple Music and Media"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Data from apps like Calendar, Contacts, Files, Health, Messages, Reminders, and Photos"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Motion and fitness data"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Additionally, you can’t use Face ID in your App Clip because the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/bundleresources/information_property_list/nsfaceidusagedescription"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " entitlement isn’t available to App Clips. However, you can use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/localauthentication"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " framework to authenticate users with Touch ID."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Reserve Certain Functionality for Your Full App",
          "anchor": "3625584"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To preserve resources and help to protect user privacy, App Clips can’t perform background activity. For example, App Clips can’t make use of the following:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Background networking with "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsurlsession"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Functionality enabled by the Background Modes capability as described in "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/usernotifications/setting_up_a_remote_notification_server/pushing_background_updates_to_your_app"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Maintaining Bluetooth connections while the App Clip is not in use"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "App Clips provide an in-the-moment experience and focus on offering the quickest possible solution to an everyday task, so some functionality works best in your full app. Reserve the following functionality for the full app:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Advanced networking features like "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/bonjour"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " and low-level networking APIs like "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/cfsocketref"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": ", or POSIX functions; instead, use "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsurlsession"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " or the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/network"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " framework."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "App extensions"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Customization and settings; for example, creation of a settings bundle"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Data handoff and document opening"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "In-app purchases"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Low-level Unix functionality; for example, BSD notifications"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Multiple scenes on iPad"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "On-demand resources"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Promoting other apps"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Registration of custom URL schemes"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Requests for user reviews of the full app by using StoreKit’s "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/storekit/skstorereviewcontroller/3566727-requestreviewinscene"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " method"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Searching for paired Bluetooth devices"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Note that an App Clip may configure Wi-Fi networks using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/bundleresources/entitlements/com_apple_developer_networking_hotspotconfiguration"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Additionally, to connect to an authentication provider, it may initialize an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/authenticationservices/aswebauthenticationsession"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " using "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/authenticationservices/aswebauthenticationsession/2990952-initwithurl"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " with a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/authenticationservices/aswebauthenticationsessionrequest/3180411-callbackurlscheme"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
